One lucky New York is waking up this morning as a millionaire. The New York State Lottery announced that a second-place winning Powerball ticket was sold in New York from Saturday's drawing.

Can You Identify These Iconic TV Show Homes?

Test your TV home knowledge! We've found iconic homes from the '60s to today. Can you guess which shows they're from?

New York State Is Home to These 2 Spaceship Houses

Not 1 but 2 "spaceship" homes in New York! One was built by a legendary actor. Let's take a look around both properties.

Gas Powered ATV/UTV Ban Looming In New York State?

The fall will be here soon and many people are heading back to the woods or trails on their ATV/UTV. But is New York State planning to ban those that are powered by gasoline?
